      <url>/2019/11/26/%E3%80%90%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%91%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>本文为作者在学习过程中对一些常用数学公式的总结，主要是为了满足个人日常的使用。如今很多网络平台已经成长为了非常重要的知识分享站，也有很多优秀的人愿意在网上分享自己的学习成果及感悟，作者由此受益良多。受到这种精神的感染，我也非常乐意成为他们中的一员，希望能对读者有些许帮助，同时也欢迎读者批评指正。</p><hr><h1 id="一、高等数学"><a href="#一、高等数学" class="headerlink" title="一、高等数学"></a>一、高等数学</h1><h2 id="Taylor展开式"><a href="#Taylor展开式" class="headerlink" title="Taylor展开式"></a>Taylor展开式</h2><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(x)=f(x_0)+f'(x_0)(x-x_0)+\frac{f^{"}(x_0)}{2!}(x-x_0)^2+\dots+\frac{f^{(n)}(x_0)}{n!}(x-x_0)^n+\dots</script><hr><h1 id="二、矩阵论"><a href="#二、矩阵论" class="headerlink" title="二、矩阵论"></a>二、矩阵论</h1><h2 id="向量范数"><a href="#向量范数" class="headerlink" title="向量范数"></a>向量范数</h2><p>对任意 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%3D%5Cleft%28%5Cxi_%7B1%7D%2C+%5Cxi_%7B2%7D%2C+%5Ccdots%2C+%5Cxi_%7Bn%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B%5Cmathrm%7BT%7D%7D+%5Cin+%5Cmathbf%7BC%7D%5E%7Bn%7D" alt="[公式]"> ，规定：</p><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=1" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7Cx%5C%7C_%7B1%7D%3D%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7Cx%5C%7C_%7B2%7D%3D%5Csqrt%7B%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7B2%7D%7D%3D%5Csqrt%7Bx%5E%7B%5Cmathrm%7BH%7D%7D+x%7D" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cinfty" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7Cx%5C%7C_%7B%5Cinfty%7D%3D%5Cmax+_%7Bk%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><hr><h2 id="矩阵范数"><a href="#矩阵范数" class="headerlink" title="矩阵范数"></a>矩阵范数</h2><p>对任意 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%3D%5Cleft%28a_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%29_%7Bn+%5Ctimes+n%7D+%5Cin+%5Cmathbf%7BC%7D%5E%7Bn+%5Ctimes+n%7D" alt="[公式]"> ，规定：</p><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=m_1" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7CA%5C%7C_%7Bm_%7B1%7D%7D%3D%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D+%5Csum_%7Bj%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7Ca_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=F" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7C%5Cboldsymbol%7BA%7D%5C%7C_%7B%5Cmathrm%7BF%7D%7D%3D%5Csqrt%7B%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7Ca_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7B2%7D%7D%3D%5Csqrt%7B%5Coperatorname%7Btr%7D%5Cleft%28%5Cboldsymbol%7BA%7D%5E%7B%5Cmathrm%7BH%7D%7D+%5Cboldsymbol%7BA%7D%5Cright%29%7D" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=m_%5Cinfty" alt="[公式]"> 范数： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7CA%5C%7C_%7Bm_%7B%5Cinfty%7D%7D%3Dn+%5Cmax+_%7Bi%2C+j%7D%5Cleft%7Ca_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><p>利用于向量的相容性，导出矩阵如下<strong>从属范数</strong>：</p><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=1" alt="[公式]"> 范数（列和范数）： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7CA%5C%7C_%7B1%7D%3D%5Cmax+_%7Bj%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7Ca_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2" alt="[公式]"> 范数（谱范数）： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7C%5Cboldsymbol%7BA%7D%5C%7C_%7B2%7D%3D%5Csqrt%7B%5Clambda_%7B1%7D%7D" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Clambda_1" alt="[公式]"> 为 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5EHA" alt="[公式]"> 的最大特征值</li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cinfty" alt="[公式]"> 范数（行和范数）： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5C%7CA%5C%7C_%7B%5Cinfty%7D%3D%5Cmax+_%7Bi%7D+%5Csum_%7Bj%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7Ca_%7Bi+j%7D%5Cright%7C" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><hr><h2 id="特殊矩阵"><a href="#特殊矩阵" class="headerlink" title="特殊矩阵"></a>特殊矩阵</h2><p><strong>常用特殊矩阵</strong></p><p><strong>正规矩阵：</strong><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=AA%5EH%3DA%5EHA" alt="[公式]"></p><ul><li>酉矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=AA%5EH%3DA%5EHA%3DI" alt="[公式]"></li><li>正交矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=AA%5ET%3DA%5ETA%3DI" alt="[公式]"> 或 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5ET%3DA%5E%7B-1%7D" alt="[公式]"></li><li>实对称矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5ET%3DA" alt="[公式]"></li><li>实反对称矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5ET%3D-A" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Hermite矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5EH%3DA" alt="[公式]"></li><li>反Hermite矩阵： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5EH%3D-A" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><p><strong>正定矩阵：</strong>满足条件 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=x%5ETAx%3E0" alt="[公式]"> 的矩阵</p><p><strong>Hilber矩阵：</strong>对称正定，严重病态，n很大时几乎奇异</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">H_n=\begin{bmatrix}1                &\frac{1}{2}        &...        &\frac{1}{n}    \\ \frac{1}{2}     &\frac{1}{3}          &...        &\frac{1}{n+1}    \\\vdots            &\vdots                &            &\vdots            \\\frac{1}{n}     &\frac{1}{n+1}      &...        &\frac{1}{2n-1}\end{bmatrix}</script><p><strong>Vandermonde矩阵：</strong>严重病态</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">V_n=\begin{bmatrix}1        &x_0        &x_0^2        &...        &x_0^2    \\ 1         &x_1          &x_1^2        &...        &x_1^2    \\\vdots    &\vdots        &            &...        &\vdots    \\1         &x_n          &x_n^2        &...        &x_n^2\end{bmatrix}</script><p><strong>Gram矩阵：</strong></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">G_n=\begin{bmatrix}(\varphi_0,\varphi_0)    &(\varphi_0,\varphi_1)    &...    &(\varphi_0,\varphi_n)    \\ (\varphi_1,\varphi_0)     &(\varphi_1,\varphi_1)     &...    &(\varphi_1,\varphi_n)    \\\vdots                    &\vdots                    &        &\vdots                    \\(\varphi_n,\varphi_0)     &(\varphi_n,\varphi_1)  &...    &(\varphi_n,\varphi_n)\end{bmatrix}</script><p><strong>特殊矩阵的性质</strong></p><ul><li>Hermite矩阵（实对称矩阵）的特征值均为实数，反Hermite矩阵（实反对称矩阵）的特征值均为零或纯虚数</li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5ETA" alt="[公式]"> 一定是一个对称正定的矩阵</li></ul><hr><h2 id="施密特标准正交化"><a href="#施密特标准正交化" class="headerlink" title="施密特标准正交化"></a>施密特标准正交化</h2><p>对于任意线形无关向量组 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Calpha_1%2C%5Calpha_2%2C...%5Calpha_n" alt="[公式]"></p><p><strong>正交化：</strong></p><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbeta_1%3D%5Calpha_1" alt="[公式]"></li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbeta_2%3D%5Calpha_2-%5Ceta_%7B2%2C1%7D%5Cbeta_1" alt="[公式]"> , <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ceta_%7B2%2C1%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B%28%5Calpha_2%2C%5Cbeta_1%29%7D%7B%28%5Cbeta_1%2C%5Cbeta_1%29%7D" alt="[公式]"></li><li>……</li><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbeta_n%3D%5Calpha_n-%5Ceta_%7Bn%2C1%7D%5Cbeta_1-%5Ceta_%7Bn%2C2%7D%5Cbeta_2-...-%5Ceta_%7Bn%2Cn-1%7D%5Cbeta_%7Bn-1%7D" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><p>其中， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ceta_%7Bn%2Cj%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B%28%5Calpha_n%2C%5Cbeta_j%29%7D%7B%28%5Cbeta_j%2C%5Cbeta_j%29%7D+%2C%EF%BC%88j%3D1%2C2%2C...%2Cn-1%EF%BC%89" alt="[公式]"></p><p><strong>单位化：</strong></p><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cgamma_1%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cbeta_1%7D%7B%5C%7C%5Cbeta_1%5C%7C_2%7D%2C%5Cgamma_2%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cbeta_2%7D%7B%5C%7C%5Cbeta_2%5C%7C_2%7D%2C...%2C%5Cgamma_n%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cbeta_n%7D%7B%5C%7C%5Cbeta_n%5C%7C_2%7D" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><p>则 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cgamma_1%2C%5Cgamma_2%2C...%2C%5Cgamma_n" alt="[公式]"> 为标准正交向量组</p><hr><h2 id="矩阵的重要变换"><a href="#矩阵的重要变换" class="headerlink" title="矩阵的重要变换"></a>矩阵的重要变换</h2><ul><li>相似： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5Csim+B%5CLeftrightarrow+P%5E%7B-1%7DAP%3DB" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=P" alt="[公式]">为由A的特征向量组成的n阶可逆矩阵</li><li>合同： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5Csimeq+B%5CLeftrightarrow+C%5ETAC%3DB" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=C" alt="[公式]">为n阶可逆矩阵</li><li>等价： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%5Ccong+B%5CLeftrightarrow+PAQ%3DB" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=P%E3%80%81Q" alt="[公式]">为可逆矩阵（有限次初等变换）</li><li>酉相似： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=U%5E%7B-1%7DAU%3DU%5E%7BH%7DAU%3DT" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=T" alt="[公式]"> 为一个上三角矩阵， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=U" alt="[公式]"> 为一个n阶酉矩阵（Schur定理）</li><li>酉等价： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=U%5EHAV%3DB" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=U%E3%80%81V" alt="[公式]">分别为m、n阶酉矩阵</li><li>Householder： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists+H%3DI-2uu%5EH%EF%BC%8Cs.t.Hx%3D%5Calpha+z" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%7C%5Calpha%7C%3D%5C%7Cx%5C%7C_2" alt="[公式]"> ， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=u%3D%5Cfrac%7Bx-%5Calpha+z%7D%7B%5C%7Cx-%5Calpha+z%5C%7C_2%7D" alt="[公式]"> ，且 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Calpha+x%5EHz" alt="[公式]"> 为实数</li><li>Givens变换： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists+T%EF%BC%8Cs.t.Tx%3D%5Calpha+z" alt="[公式]"> ，其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%7C%5Calpha%7C%3D%5C%7Cx%5C%7C_2" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Hessenberg变换：<ul><li>Ver1： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28%5Cprod_%7Bi%7DH_i%29A%28%5Cprod_%7Bi%7DH_i%29+%3DU%5E%7BH%7DAU%3DH" alt="[公式]"> ,其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=H" alt="[公式]"> 为一个次上三角矩阵， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=H_i" alt="[公式]"> 为Householder矩阵</li><li>Ver2： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28%5Cprod_%7Bi%7DT_i%29A%28%5Cprod_%7Bi%7DT_i%29%5EH+%3DU%5E%7BH%7DAU%3DH" alt="[公式]"> ,其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=H" alt="[公式]"> 为一个次上三角矩阵， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=T_i" alt="[公式]"> 为Givens矩阵</li></ul></li></ul><hr><h2 id="矩阵函数"><a href="#矩阵函数" class="headerlink" title="矩阵函数"></a>矩阵函数</h2><p><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cbegin%7Barray%7D%7Bll%7D%7B%5Cmathrm%7Be%7D%5E%7B%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%7D%3D%5Csum_%7Bk%3D0%7D%5E%7B%2B%5Cinfty%7D+%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bk+%21%7D+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%5E%7Bk%7D%7D+%26+%7B%5Cleft%28%5Cforall+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D+%5Cin+%5Cmathrm%7BC%7D%5E%7B%5Cmathrm%7Bn%7D+%5Ctimes+n%7D%5Cright%29%7D+%5C%5C++%7B%5Csin+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%3D%5Csum_%7Bk%3D0%7D%5E%7B%2B%5Cinfty%7D+%5Cfrac%7B%28-1%29%5E%7Bk%7D%7D%7B%282+k%2B1%29+%21%7D+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%5E%7B2+k%2B1%7D%7D+%26+%7B%5Cleft%28%5Cforall+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D+%5Cin+%5Cmathrm%7BC%7D%5E%7Bn+%5Ctimes+n%7D%5Cright%29%7D+%5C%5C++%7B%5Ccos+A%3D%5Csum_%7Bk%3D0%7D%5E%7B%2B%5Cinfty%7D+%5Cfrac%7B%28-1%29%5E%7Bk%7D%7D%7B%282+k%29+%21%7D+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%5E%7B2+k%7D%7D+%26+%7B%5Cleft%28%5Cforall+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D+%5Cin+%5Cmathrm%7BC%7D%5E%7Bn+%5Ctimes+n%7D%5Cright%29%7D+%5C%5C++%7B%28%5Cmathrm%7BI%7D-%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%29%5E%7B-1%7D%3D%7D++%7B%5Csum_%7Bk%3D0%7D%5E%7B%2B%5Cinfty%7D+%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%5E%7Bk%7D+%7D%26%7B%5Cquad%28%5Crho%28%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%29%3C1%29%7D+%5C%5C++%7B%5Cln+%28%5Cmathrm%7BI%7D%2B%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%29%3D%7D+%7B%5Csum_%7Bk%3D0%7D%5E%7B%2B%5Cinfty%7D+%5Cfrac%7B%28-1%29%5E%7Bk%7D%7D%7Bk%2B1%7D+A%5E%7Bk%2B1%7D%7D%26%7B%5Cquad%28%5Crho%28%5Cmathrm%7BA%7D%29%3C1%29%7D%5Cend%7Barray%7D" alt="[公式]"></p><p>其中，称 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=e%5EA" alt="[公式]"> 为矩阵指数函数， <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28I-A%29%5E%7B-1%7D" alt="[公式]"> 为Neumann级数</p><h2 id="二阶矩阵求逆公式"><a href="#二阶矩阵求逆公式" class="headerlink" title="二阶矩阵求逆公式"></a><strong>二阶矩阵求逆公式</strong></h2><ul><li><img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%7B%5Cleft%28+%7B%5Cbegin%7Barray%7D%7B%2A%7B20%7D%7Bc%7D%7D+%7B%5Crm%7Ba%7D%7D%26b%5C%5C+c%26d+%5Cend%7Barray%7D%7D+%5Cright%29%5E%7B+-+1%7D%7D+%3D+%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%7Bad+-+bc%7D%7D%5Cleft%28+%7B%5Cbegin%7Barray%7D%7B%2A%7B20%7D%7Bc%7D%7D+d%26%7B+-+b%7D%5C%5C+%7B+-+c%7D%26a+%5Cend%7Barray%7D%7D+%5Cright%29%2Cad+-+bc+%5Cne+0" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><hr><h1 id="三、不等式"><a href="#三、不等式" class="headerlink" title="三、不等式"></a>三、不等式</h1><h2 id="柯西-施瓦茨不等式："><a href="#柯西-施瓦茨不等式：" class="headerlink" title="柯西-施瓦茨不等式："></a>柯西-施瓦茨不等式：</h2><ul><li>Ver1: <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cleft%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5Cleft%7C%5Ceta_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D+%5Cleqslant%5Cleft%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%5Cleft%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Ceta_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright%29" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Ver2： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cleft%7C+%7B%7Bx%5EH%7Dy%7D+%5Cright%7C+%5Cle+%5Cleft%5C%7C+x+%5Cright%5C%7C%5Cleft%5C%7C+y+%5Cright%5C%7C%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%28x%2Cy+%5Cin+%7BR%5En%7D%29+" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Ver3： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%7B%5Ceta+_k%7D%29%5E2+%5Cleq+n%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%7B%5Ceta%5E2+_k%7D" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Ver4：$(f+g,f+g)^{\frac{1}{2}}\leq(f,f)^{\frac{1}{2}}+(g,g)^{\frac{1}{2}}$</li><li>Ver5：$(f,g)\leq (f,f)^{\frac{1}{2}}(g,g)^{\frac{1}{2}}$</li></ul><h2 id="Holder不等式："><a href="#Holder不等式：" class="headerlink" title="Holder不等式："></a><strong>Holder不等式：</strong></h2><ul><li>Ver1： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D+%5C%7C+%5Ceta_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C+%5Cleqslant%5Cleft%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Cxi_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7Bp%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bp%7D%7D%5Cleft%28%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%5Cleft%7C%5Ceta_%7Bk%7D%5Cright%7C%5E%7Bq%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bq%7D%7D" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><p>其中 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p%3E1%2C+q%3E1" alt="[公式]"> 且 <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bp%7D%2B%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bq%7D%3D1" alt="[公式]"></p><hr><h2 id="min-max不等式："><a href="#min-max不等式：" class="headerlink" title="min-max不等式："></a>min-max不等式：</h2><ul><li>Ver1： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=l%5Ccdot+%5Cmax+%5C%7B+m%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%2C%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+n%5C%7D++%5Cle+%5Cmax+%5C%7B+m%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%2C%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+l%5C%7D++%5Ccdot+%5Cmax+%5C%7B+n%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%2C%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+%7B%5Ckern+1pt%7D+l%5C%7D+" alt="[公式]"></li><li>Ver2： <img src="https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cmax+%5C%7B+%7Bx_1%7D+%2B+%7By_1%7D%2C%7Bx_2%7D+%2B+%7By_2%7D%5C%7D++%5Cle+%5Cmax+%5C%7B+%7Bx_1%7D+%2B+%7Bx_2%7D%5C%7D++%2B+%5Cmax+%5C%7B+%7By_1%7D+%2B+%7By_2%7D%5C%7D+" alt="[公式]"></li></ul><hr><h1 id="四、代数"><a href="#四、代数" class="headerlink" title="四、代数"></a>四、代数</h1><h2 id="最大公约数"><a href="#最大公约数" class="headerlink" title="最大公约数"></a>最大公约数</h2><ul><li>图解法</li><li>欧几里得算法：辗转相除法（算法鼻祖）</li></ul><h2 id="贝祖数"><a href="#贝祖数" class="headerlink" title="贝祖数"></a>贝祖数</h2><ul><li>$ax+by=m$有整数解的充要条件：m为a、b最大公约数的整数倍</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
